  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_1' aria-label=\" Union of India versus M/s Kamakhya Transport Pvt. Ltd. Etc. Etc. pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('1','2025','2025_7_346_353','2025INSC805'); ><font size='4'> <strong>UNION OF INDIA<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>M/S KAMAKHYA TRANSPORT PVT. LTD. ETC. ETC. </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 7 S.C.R. 346</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 805</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010002762025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : SANJAY KAROL<sup style=\"color: #268e97;font-size: 22px;top: 0;\" class=\"tooltip-sup\" data-tooltip=\"Author\">*</sup>, PRASHANT KUMAR MISHRA</strong><br> Issue for Consideration Whether the Courts below had rightly held that the Railway authorities could not have raised the demand notice after the delivery of goods. Headnotes&dagger; Railways Act, 1989 &ndash; s.66 &ndash; Power to require statement relating to the description of goods &ndash; notices alleging misdeclaration of goods, for consignments sent through the Railways &ndash; Respondents paid the demands raised but sought refund of the amount paid contending that the demand notices issued after the delivery of the goods were illegal &ndash; Claim allowed by Railway Tribunal<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 05-06-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> CIVIL APPEAL No. 7376/2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Appeal(s) allowed</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 2 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('1','2025','2025_7_346_353','2025INSC805','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('1','2025','2025_7_346_353','2025INSC805','H'); ><i class='fas fa-file-alt me-2'></i>HTML view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_flip('1','2025','2025_7_346_353','2025INSC805');><i class='fas fa-book-open me-2' ></i>Flip view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_pdf('1','2025','2025_7_346_353','2025INSC805','N'); ><i class='fas fa-file-pdf me-2'></i>PDF</a></div></div>",
